headline: JPMorgan hires former HSBC dealmaker Kamal Jabre to drive EMEA growth
summary: Alongside Jabre, the bank also named insider Marc Pandraud, who joined JPMorgan from Deutsche Bank in 2016, as M&A Vice Chair.  The two will collaborate closely with JPMorgan's local industry, country and M&A teams to expand its franchise in EMEA, the memo added.
